        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那将是我与郎君共度的时光，当然……得好好准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来我也得精心准备，作为给你的回应才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星琼弦",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯！",
        "disable": 0
    },
